n International Driver&#x2019;s Permit if you&#x2019;re a non-EU citizen driving in Spain. You will be asked to present this to the rental agency, as well as the Spanish police in the event you&#x2019;re stopped while driving. An International Driver&#x2019;s Permit costs just 15 USD and is valid for one year. <a href=\"https:\/\/internationaldrivingpermit.org\/how-to-apply\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">You can arrange yours here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5.jpg\" alt=\"how to rent a car spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"249\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to rent a car spain\" class=\"wp-image-86560 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1412px) 100vw, 1412px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5.jpg 1412w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-441x600.jpg 441w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-596x810.jpg 596w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-249x338.jpg 249w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-120x163.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-565x768.jpg 565w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25111622\/car-rental-spain-5-753x1024.jpg 753w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/251116