included (so no surprises when collecting your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8.jpg\" alt=\"renting a car in spain madrid\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"renting a car in spain madrid\" class=\"wp-image-86569 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25113155\/car-rental-spain-8-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploa