            <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25153910\/car-rental-spain-1-1-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25153910\/car-rental-spain-1-1-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Renting a Car in Spain in 2022: All you need to know\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>When you opt for one of these roads, you can pay the toll in cash, by credit card, or with the electronic device Via-T. The toll routes in Spain typically cost between 5 and 30 EUR depending on the distance you travel on the route and the location of the Autopista.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145747\/car-rental-spain-12.jpg\" alt=\"roads spain renting a car\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"roads spain renting a car\" class=\"wp-image-86611 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145747\/car-rental-spain-12.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145747\/car-rental-spain-12-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145747\/car-rental-spain-12-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145747\/car-rental-spain-12-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145747\/car-rental-spain-12-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourh