as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/things-to-do-madrid\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Madrid<\/a>, don&#x2019;t even allow traffic to enter the city&#x2019;s historical center to reduce pollution.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> If you&#x2019;re visiting one of the bigger cities, try to park your car outside the center and take public transportation instead to get around. Spain&#x2019;s urban public transport is quite good and includes a mix of metros, tramways, and buses. This is often also cheaper as the closer you get to the center of the city, the more expensive car parking becomes.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29132419\/madrid-35.jpg\" alt=\"rent a car madrid spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"rent a car madrid spain\" class=\"wp-image-79227 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29132419\/madrid-35.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29132419\/madrid-35-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/29132419\/madrid-35-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/