019;s mountains in the winter, your car might require snow chains. When picking up your rental car in Spain, make sure to ask the agency about it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2.jpg\" alt=\"driving in spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"250\" height=\"338\" alt=\"driving in spain\" class=\"wp-image-84015 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1422px) 100vw, 1422px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2.jpg 1422w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-444x600.jpg 444w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-600x810.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-250x338.jpg 250w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-133x180.jpg 133w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-569x768.jpg 569w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-758x1024.jpg 758w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-800x1080.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-1067x1440.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20111918\/cadiz-spain-Olvera-2-300x405.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha