oads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25145729\/car-rental-spain-11.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You will have to sign a document called the check-out form. If your rental car has any scratches or other types of damage, which isn&#x2019;t uncommon in Spain, check if they are listed on the form. If they&#x2019;re not, make sure to point them out to the employee and have them noted down before signing the check-out form. This form will also list the mileage and the amount of fuel the car has upon pickup time. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you want to be absolutely certain that everything is logged, take some photos or videos of the rental car&#x2019;s noted damages, the amount of fuel in the tank, and the previous mileage of the car.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Rent a car in Spain via <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and insurances are included (so no surprises when collecting your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/25150739\/car-rental-spain-13.jpg\" alt=\"renting a car in granada spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"renting a car in granada spain\" class=\"wp-image-86614 lazypreload\" data-